==Description==

The [[File:Spreadsheet_AlignRight.svg|24px]] '''Spreadsheet AlignRight''' tool aligns the contents of selected cells to the right.

==Usage==

# Make sure there is an active [[Spreadsheet_CreateSheet|spreadsheet]].
# Select one or more cells.
# There are several ways to invoke the tool:
#* Press the {{Button|[[File:Spreadsheet_AlignRight.svg|16px]] [[Spreadsheet_AlignRight|Align Right]]}} button.
#* Select the {{MenuCommand|Spreadsheet → Alignment → [[File:Spreadsheet_AlignRight.svg|16px]] Align Right}} option from the menu.


